addWeapon 
Behavior: local 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Add a weapon to a unit. Infantry units can only carry a specific 
 number of weapons, once the weapon slots are filled, any further 
 addWeapon commands are ignored.  
Syntax:  
 unitName addWeapon weaponName 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object - unit to add the weapon to 
weaponName: String - weapon name. See the topic Category:Weapons for reference about possible values. 
Return Value: 
 Nothing